  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_pathologist">Pathologist</xref>
 is a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_pathologist">Pathologist</xref>
 works with 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_general_practitioner">GENERAL PRACTITIONERS</xref>, scientists, 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_nurse">NURSES</xref>
 and 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONALS</xref>
 in hospitals and 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_gp_practice">GP Practices</xref>
 to diagnose, treat and prevent illness.        </p>
      <p>
For further information on 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_pathologist">Pathologists</xref>, see the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_royal_college_of_pathologists">Royal College of Pathologists</xref>
 website at: 
              <xref href="https://www.rcpath.org/discover-pathology/what-is-pathology.html"
               scope="external"
               format="html">What is pathology?</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
